					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13445547#post-4695962</guid>
				<title>Author Post</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13445547/scp-5089#post-4695962</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 21 Jun 2020 22:24:20 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Bard Bard</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5926560</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is it - my first SCP! If you read this little work of mine, thank you so much, I hope you enjoyed and that it proved worthy of your time!</p> <p>This SCP is inspired by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/avelon21" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5341612&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592827331" alt="Avelon21" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5341612)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/avelon21" >Avelon21</a></span>'s <a href="http://wanderers-library.wikidot.com/a-cromwell">&quot;A Cromwell&quot;</a> over on the Wanderers' Library. A massive thank you to them for both writing it and allowing me to exand upon their work with SCP-5089.</p> <p>This article was written for the <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/exquisite-corpse-contest">2020 Exquisite Corpse Contest</a>, with the conprocs being written by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/strayghost" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6116198&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592827331" alt="StrayGhost" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6116198)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/strayghost" >StrayGhost</a></span>.</p> <p>Additionally, a big thank you to my critters <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/avelon21" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5341612&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592827331" alt="Avelon21" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5341612)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/avelon21" >Avelon21</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sebarus" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2341265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592827331" alt="Sebarus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2341265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sebarus" >Sebarus</a></span>, without whoms support and critique this article wouldn't be.</p> <p>The image is <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Pica_pica_skull.jpg">&quot;Pica_pica_skull&quot;</a> by Dunnykin, licensed under CC BY 2.0. The paper texture is by <a href="https://www.deviantart.com/jojo-ojoj">Jojo-ojoJ</a> on Deviantart, licensed under CC BY 3.0.</p> 
				 	]]>
